NAME
	trim_str - remove extra whitespace

SYNOPSIS
	string trim_str(string str);

DESCRIPTION
	Replaces all whitespace with a single blank space.

RETURN VALUE
	The string with whitespace replaced with a single black space.

SEE ALSO
	afun/empty_str, afun/fmt_str, afun/pad_string_left,
	afun/replace_string, afun/rexplode, afun/strcmp, afun/strstr,
